            <org>Obstetrical and Abdominal Division</org></p>
        <p> and nearly 200 County Medical Societies</p>
        <p> 150 Birth Control Clinics established</p>
        <p> Birth Control indicates is keynote new social and moral awakening </p>
        <p> not only health and economic <supplied resp="MSPP">expedient</supplied></p>
        <p> Social principle interlocked spiritual advance of nation and the race</p>
        <p> Birth control conscious culture - prevent</p>
        <p> prevent not destroy</p>
        <p> control not limit</p>
        <p> conscious control deliberate intentional </p>
        <p> choice instead of chance</p>
        <p> positive instead of negative control</p>
        <p> Why control birth rate?</p>
        <p> Two problems confront one civilization</p>
        <p> 1 Pressure of population on social system</p>
        <p> 2 Reconciling humanitarian efforts with race <supplied resp="MSPP"
                >improvements</supplied></p>
