            <person reg="Myers, William Starr">William Starr Myers</person>. 85 20 (105)</p>
        <p> Professor <person reg="Ross, Edward A.">Ross</person> 150,000 babies born every day</p>
        <p> 100,000 babies die every day</p>
        <p> 50,000</p>
